idl_progs
useful idl scripts for use with ExoRT

cloudoptics_mie.pro      -- create custom 1d profile for ExoCAM
corrk2netcdf.pro         -- convert HELIOS-K formated output text files
getcolumn.pro            -- grab single specified column from CESM model output and create 1D input file
makeCIA.pro              -- create CIA files formatted for ExoRT
makecolumn.pro           -- create a new column to test in ExoRT
makeMTCKD.pro            -- create MT_CKD H2O self continuun formatted for ExoRT
makeStellarSpectrum.pro  -- create stellar spectra formatted for ExoRT
plotprofile.pro          -- plot vertical profiles from 1D output
plotspectra_1d.pro       -- plot spectral radiance from 1D output
plotstellar.pro          -- plot stellar spectra from existing ExoRT files
mie_single.pro           -- standard mie code for spherical cloud and aerosolparticles


